The paper focuses on the problem of robot navigation, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The proposed learning architecture involves reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of cloud robotic systems suggests a focus on distributed systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the experiments involve visual perception and image processing, which are topics in computer vision (cs.CV).
